==Changes==
{{Subject changes header}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 28 April 2021
|update = Arceuus Spellbook Beta and A Kingdom Divided Preparation
|change = Some new counters have been added to the Collection Log, including the number of Tempoross Reward Permits claimed, and Spoils Of War opened in Soul Wars!
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 14 April 2021
|update = Below Ice Mountain
|change = <nowiki />
*Brimhaven graceful pieces will now be correctly counted within the Collection Log on log-in.
*Players can now search for all boss categories in the Collection Log.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 7 April 2021
|update = Collection Log Improvements and The Last of Poll 74
|change = <nowiki />
*The Collection Log now has a search function.
*A new counter shows the total number of unique items obtained.
*Added a toggleable chat/popup notification when a new item has been added to the collection log.
*The colour of each section of the log changes based on its completed status.
*Different boss modes now have separate kill counts on their respective interfaces (Dagannoth Kings, Gauntlet, Chambers of Xeric).
*Gnome Restaurant has a delivery count at the top of its section.
*Volcanic Mine rewards have been added.
*Third age and gilded items can now be found in the "Rares" tabs for each clue scroll.
*A Brimhaven Agility section has been added to the minigames tab.
*Pirate Hook has been moved from Underwater Agility to the Brimhaven Agility section.
*Merfolk Trident has been added to the Misc section.
*Marks of Grace have been added to the Rooftop Agility section.
*Third age pieces now have their own separate tab.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 25 July 2019
|update = Song of the Elves
|change =
[[Crystal seed]]s were removed from [[Zulrah]]'s drop table and subsequently removed from its section within the collection log. Drops from [[The Gauntlet]], [[Zalcano]], [[Prifddinas]] were added to the collection log.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 4 July 2019
|update = Forthos Dungeon
|change = Drops from [[Sarachnis]] were added to the collection log.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 25 April 2019
|update = QoL Changes and Warding Feedback
|change = The [[Spiked manacles]] and [[Climbing boots (g)]] entries were switched around.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 7 February 2019
|update = X Marks The Spot
|change = The collection log now tracks [[My Notes]] correctly.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 31 January 2019
|update = Chambers of Xeric, Kebos, and Collection Log Changes
|change = Several additions to existing categories were added, as well as four new categories: [[Rooftop Agility]], [[Creature Creation]], [[Fossil island note book|Fossil Island Notes]] and [[My Notes]].
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 13 December 2018
|update = Christmas Event 2018
|change = Several additions to existing categories were added, as well as four new categories: [[Chompy bird hat]]s and [[Random event]] rewards.
}}
{{Subject changes
|date = 10 December 2018
|change = The collection log was made available to [[free-to-play]] players.
}}
{{Subject changes footer}}

